reviewText: I absolutely love this series! Whoever thought to make a kids show with a bunch of talking sex toys is a freaking genius! 10/10
My granddaughter thinks this is hilarious.  She sings and dances with it.
These are such cute stories! I bought these for the preschool class at church and they really enjoy them.
They were very accurate in sending the package on time. My daughter is enjoying the movies VERY MUCH
